      <event start="T1729-852" end="T1730-679">Ne, pač ... </event>
      <event start="T1749-296" end="T386">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T386" end="T1754-708">no to. </event>
      <event start="T1759-248" end="T1762-050">Pač nas je bvo, mislim, da nekej čez deset </event>
      <event start="T1762-050" end="T1762-707">in pol s ble itak tri tablce </event>
      <event start="T1762-707" end="T1764-755">in itak pač ... </event>
      <event start="T1764-755" end="T389">Čist, čist na strani se itak niso čuli vmes </event>
      <event start="T389" end="T491">in je s() </event>
      <event start="T491" end="T1775-014">in je folk pač naročvou isto zadevo </event>
      <event start="T1775-014" end="T1782-889">in na koncu, ko smo bl že vsi pač dan, dan, smo dobli pač štirkrat en() en() eno stvar. </event>
      <event start="T1782-889" end="T390">In si bil sam t@k: </event>
      <event start="T390" end="T1787-082">"Pa, pa za koga pa zaka?" </event>
