      <event start="T145" end="T665-974">skenclaš. </event>
      <event start="T665-974" end="T667-421">Daj no. </event>
      <event start="T675-419" end="T678-138">A, a, a bejži. </event>
      <event start="T678-635" end="T680-155">N() ne bi si mislil. </event>
      <event start="T681-890" end="T683-763">Od kdaj naprej pa? </event>
      <event start="T685-831" end="T686-502">Mislim, </event>
      <event start="T686-502" end="T687-356">Jesus. </event>
      <event start="T728-463" end="T162">Ja čakaj, </event>
      <event start="T162" end="T457">kaj pa pol, ko si nazaj prišla, </event>
      <event start="T457" end="T733-961">ste mogli eee za faks kako poročilo narediti? </event>
      <event start="T733-961" end="T735-72">Predstaviti ... </event>
      <event start="T736-734" end="T737-801">Ali je bilo to to? </event>
      <event start="T769-315" end="T168">O fak, </event>
      <event start="T168" end="T169">ja, </event>
      <event start="T169" end="T772-68">kje sploh začeti? </event>
      <event start="T772-68" end="T773-888">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T773-888" end="T775-605">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T775-605" end="T776-85">Eee ... </event>
      <event start="T776-85" end="T778-180">[glas] </event>
      <event start="T778-180" end="T782-635">Mmm mislim eem ... </event>
      <event start="T782-635" end="T786-495">De() decembra še nisem vedel glih, kaj bo z novim letom. </event>
      <event start="T786-495" end="T170">Eee takrat, ko bi mogel dobiti šiht, </event>
      <event start="T170" end="T793-849">so pol e() enega drugega vzeli za senior pozicijo. </event>
      <event start="T793-849" end="T797-802">Eem ... [glas] </event>
      <event start="T797-802" end="T171">Pol pa, pol pa itak pač, </event>
      <event start="T171" end="T172">ko ne veš, kaj bo čez par mesecev, si pač tako ono, </event>
      <event start="T172" end="T804-422">pač bo, kaj b() ... </event>
      <event start="T804-422" end="T173">Pol pa itak prvi dan po novem letu prid() pridem v pisarno, </event>
      <event start="T173" end="T810-423">pride ta novi, </event>
      <event start="T810-423" end="T174">pa ga šef predstavi </event>
      <event start="T174" end="T813-48">pa reče: </event>
      <event start="T813-48" end="T175">"No, </event>
      <event start="T175" end="T176">toti, toti, tole je vaš študent, </event>
      <event start="T176" end="T818-149">zaenkrat še. </event>
      <event start="T818-149" end="T821-918">Delamo na tem, da bo čim prej redno zaposlen." </event>
      <event start="T821-918" end="T823-668">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T823-668" end="T178">Eem </event>
      <event start="T178" end="T177">pol pa ja, </event>
