      <event start="T1897-048" end="T1899-209">se ne moreš izogniti. </event>
      <event start="T1903-24" end="T1907-15">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1907-15" end="T1910-047">Posodo pač v pomivalcu. </event>
      <event start="T1912-126" end="T1913-71">Yup. </event>
