      <event start="T1555-504" end="T356">Ne vem točno s čem, </event>
      <event start="T356" end="T1558-46">ampak jaz sem ga z soli. </event>
      <event start="T1558-46" end="T357">In pol pa pripraviš nadev. </event>
      <event start="T357" end="T1564-837">Js osebno mam ful rada tuno, </event>
      <event start="T1564-837" end="T1569-301">eee </event>
      <event start="T1569-301" end="T358">tak da nardim pol tuna pa majoneza pa tako pekočo omako, </event>
      <event start="T358" end="T359">ko se ji reče sirača, </event>
      <event start="T359" end="T1575-191">dam tud n@t@r, </event>
      <event start="T1575-191" end="T483">da je mal bolj zanimiv okus, </event>
      <event start="T483" end="T1579-024">da ni sam majoneza pa tuna. </event>
      <event start="T1579-024" end="T1584-296">In v bistvu pol vzameš eno kepo riža, ko je že ohlajen, </event>
      <event start="T1584-296" end="T484">ne, ne vročeg(), ne, </event>
      <event start="T484" end="T360">ne vrečega riža eee met v roki, </event>
      <event start="T360" end="T1590-077">zarad tega k se boš opeko. </event>
      <event start="T1590-077" end="T361">Eem </event>
      <event start="T361" end="T1593-663">ampak v bistvu vzameš kepo riža, </event>
      <event start="T1593-663" end="T1596-15">jo nardiš v tako, </event>
      <event start="T1596-15" end="T1598-379">pač, </event>
      <event start="T1598-379" end="T485">fa(), </event>
      <event start="T485" end="T1600-503">js ne znam slovensko. </event>
      <event start="T1600-503" end="T1602-644">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1602-644" end="T1603-91">Flet. [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T1603-91" end="T1604-625">Flet. </event>
      <event start="T1605-308" end="T362">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T362" end="T1606-24">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1606-24" end="T1610-294">Nardiš eee v bistvu sploščiš t@ti riž. </event>
      <event start="T1610-294" end="T1616-751">In pol vzameš eno m() malo žličko t@tega nadeva, ko si ga naredu. </event>
      <event start="T1616-751" end="T363">Ga daš na sredino riža </event>
      <event start="T363" end="T1623-109">in pol prvo nardiš vse to t@k v tako kroglco, </event>
      <event start="T1623-109" end="T1626-421">t@k da more b@t nadev na sredini t@te kroglce. </event>
      <event start="T1626-421" end="T364">In pol nardiš v bistvu v trikotnik, </event>
      <event start="T364" end="T486">in to je najbolj značilna stvar za onigiri, </event>
      <event start="T486" end="T1633-439">to, da je v trikotniku nareto. </event>
      <event start="T1633-439" end="T1636-625">In pol dobiš še alge, </event>
      <event start="T1636-625" end="T1639-889">t@te alge, ko so po navadi tud okolo sušija. </event>
      <event start="T1639-889" end="T366">Eee </event>
      <event start="T366" end="T365">dobiš alge </event>
      <event start="T365" end="T1643-912">pa pol v bistvu zaviješ. </event>
      <event start="T1645-295" end="T367">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T367" end="T1646-492">posušene alge. </event>
      <event start="T1647-586" end="T370">Ja ja ja ja ja, </event>
      <event start="T370" end="T369">pač uni lis() listi, </event>
      <event start="T369" end="T1650-468">isto ko pač maš za suši, </event>
      <event start="T1650-468" end="T1654-053">če si že kdaj suši j() jedo. </event>
      <event start="T1658-838" end="T1660-781">A U Suši, </event>
      <event start="T1660-781" end="T1661-777">ko lahk poješ kejkr hoč()? </event>
      <event start="T1662-957" end="T487">In, </event>
      <event start="T487" end="T1664-238">k@k ti je bvo? </event>
      <event start="T1670-354" end="T1671-99">Kdaj si, </event>
      <event start="T1671-99" end="T374">kdaj si pa bil? </event>
      <event start="T374" end="T1674-864">Zarad tega ker mi smo tud bli ... </event>
      <event start="T1674-864" end="T1675-727">mislim ... </event>
      <event start="T1675-727" end="T1677-103">T@ti pond@lk? </event>
      <event start="T1678-543" end="T488">Mi smo, </event>
      <event start="T488" end="T375">kdaj smo pa mi bli? </event>
      <event start="T375" end="T376">Mi smo bli pa prej(), prejšnjo ned() ... šestega, </event>
      <event start="T376" end="T1684-874">v nedelo. </event>
      <event start="T1684-874" end="T1686-524">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1686-524" end="T1693-412">Z z s(), z sestro in njeno sestro in z sestrinim stricom. </event>
      <event start="T1705-745" end="T1707-182">A ste mogli kaj z()... </event>
      <event start="T1719-097" end="T1721-568">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1721-568" end="T1728-891">Mi smo, mi smo se isto mogli ful potrudit, da smo na koncu poje(), pojedli vse, kar smo si naročli. </event>
      <event start="T1728-891" end="T1729-852">Zard tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1729-852" end="T1730-679">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T1730-679" end="T384">od kod so vs() vs() vsi uni krožniki pršli, </event>
      <event start="T384" end="T1738-118">ampak u, kr, zarad tega ker </event>
      <event start="T1738-118" end="T385">ne vem, </event>
      <event start="T385" end="T1740-898">neki naročiš v prvi rundi, </event>
      <event start="T1740-898" end="T1747-656">in pol ti šele po, po tem, ko si ti drugo na run(), rundo naroču, ti pridu uno, ka si naroču v prvi rundi. </event>
      <event start="T1747-656" end="T1754-708">In pol si sam zmeden, od kje je pršva t@ta rolica pa kje je pršva una rolica. </event>
      <event start="T1754-708" end="T387">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T387" end="T388">tak da mi smo meli is(), isti problem, </event>
      <event start="T388" end="T1759-248">ampak smo vse pojedli. </event>
      <event start="T1762-050" end="T1762-707">Des() ... </event>
      <event start="T1787-082" end="T1788-198">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1788-198" end="T391">K@k, </event>
      <event start="T391" end="T1791-166">a to ste šli z šihtom? </event>
      <event start="T1795-429" end="T393">Aaa, </event>
      <event start="T393" end="T1797-737">okej. </event>
      <event start="T1797-737" end="T394">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T394" end="T1806-333">drugač prej ko sma se tud pogovarjava o stanovanju, sn te hotva vprašat mal več o t@tem stanovanju oziroma </event>
      <event start="T1806-333" end="T395">zdej ko maš svoje stanovanje, </event>
      <event start="T395" end="T1811-515">ka ti je najboljš pucat v t@tem stanovanju </event>
      <event start="T1811-515" end="T396">oziroma ka naj() n() ka ti je najhujš pucat, </event>
      <event start="T396" end="T1815-953">lahk tud to. </event>
      <event start="T1815-953" end="T1817-789">Pa k@k to spučeš pol. </event>
      <event start="T1822-797" end="T1823-517">Ne. </event>
      <event start="T1828-898" end="T1830-557">Absolutne cvetke. </event>
      <event start="T1830-557" end="T1832-358">Upam, da čujeta to. </event>
      <event start="T1862-036" end="T1862-719">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1865-643" end="T1866-644">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T1866-644" end="T411">No, </event>
      <event start="T411" end="T1869-575">ka ka pa najrajš pučeš? </event>
      <event start="T1899-209" end="T417">K@k pa spučeš posodo </event>
      <event start="T417" end="T1903-24">pa k@k spučeš tla? </event>
      <event start="T1910-047" end="T1912-126">Pomivalc maš? </event>
      <event start="T1913-71" end="T1915-255">Ooo. </event>
      <event start="T1915-255" end="T1916-347">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1917-066" end="T418">Čaki, </event>
      <event start="T418" end="T419">a preden daš v pomivalc, a prvo spereš dov </event>
      <event start="T419" end="T1922-407">al sam daš n@t@r? </event>
      <event start="T1922-407" end="T1924-703">To je ful pomembno. </event>
      <event start="T1926-514" end="T1927-077">Meni. </event>
      <event start="T1929-303" end="T1929-954">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1942-906" end="T1944-174">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T1958-729" end="T1959-696">Eem ... </event>
      <event start="T1959-696" end="T1961-631">[premor] </event>
      <event start="T1961-631" end="T1962-470">Ka pa tla? </event>
      <event start="T1965-216" end="T1966-837">Podn. </event>
      <event start="T1970-3" end="T426">Rumba. </event>
      <event start="T426" end="T1972-397">A bi jo mel? </event>
      <event start="T2001-764" end="T433">Mmm. </event>
      <event start="T433" end="T2003-677">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T2023-74" end="T2025-262">Okej. </event>
      <event start="T2026-923" end="T2027-331">Jej. </event>
    </tier>
    <tier id="TIE4" speaker="ROG-dialog-0049" category="norm" type="t" display-name="ROG-dialog-0049 [norm]">
      <event start="T7-327" end="T4">Eem, </event>
      <event start="T4" end="T5">ja, </event>
      <event start="T5" end="T10-7">je bilo kar lepo. </event>
      <event start="T10-7" end="T6">Eem, </event>
      <event start="T6" end="T7">šli smo iz Zagreba, </event>
      <event start="T7" end="T18-954">torej smo leteli iz Zagreba do Turčije. </event>
      <event start="T18-954" end="T8">Pač do Istanbula </event>
      <event start="T8" end="T24-117">in pol smo šli še od Istanbula do Osake. </event>
      <event start="T24-117" end="T25-135">Mmm. </event>
      <event start="T26-515" end="T28-703">Do Zagreba sem prišla v bistvu ... </event>
      <event start="T28-703" end="T441">Ttt ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T441" end="T9">to je ful zanimivo, </event>
      <event start="T9" end="T35-966">ampak sem dejansko šla od eee iz Ljubljane do Pragerskega. </event>
      <event start="T35-966" end="T10">Eem </event>
      <event start="T10" end="T11">pa tam me je pol moj prijatelj pobral </event>
      <event start="T11" end="T442">in sem šla pol sm() smo šli z avtom do Zagreba. </event>
      <event start="T442" end="T43-813">[smeh] </event>
      <event start="T47-687" end="T48-133">Ja z ... </event>
      <event start="T48-133" end="T14">ja, ja, </event>
      <event start="T14" end="T13">z vlakom sem šla, </event>
      <event start="T13" end="T50-642">ja. </event>
      <event start="T51-553" end="T52-69">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T52-69" end="T15">No, </event>
      <event start="T15" end="T16">eem, </event>
      <event start="T16" end="T17">tako da sem en dan prej spakirala, </event>
      <event start="T17" end="T18">zaradi tega ker se prej nisem lotila pakirati, </event>
      <event start="T18" end="T60-812">zaradi tega ker sem malo neumna. </event>
      <event start="T60-812" end="T19">Ampak okej, </event>
      <event start="T19" end="T64-389">to bomo pustili za sabo. </event>
      <event start="T64-389" end="T20">Eem, </event>
      <event start="T20" end="T21">no, </event>
      <event start="T21" end="T22">ampak sem lepo spakirala, </event>
      <event start="T22" end="T69-347">se mi zdi. </event>
      <event start="T71-301" end="T73-284">Klasik(). [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T73-284" end="T23">Pozabila nisem kaj, </event>
      <event start="T23" end="T24">zaradi tega ker sem eem, </event>
      <event start="T24" end="T81-397">te ko sem pakirala, sem Urško p() ... mojo sestro poklicala. [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T81-397" end="T26">Eem pa sem jo vprašala </event>
      <event start="T26" end="T27">oziroma sem ji rekla, da mi naj da en seznam, kaj vse ne smem pozabiti </event>
      <event start="T27" end="T89-297">oziroma kaj vse moram imeti s sabo. </event>
      <event start="T89-297" end="T91-191">Tako da mi je ona pomagala. </event>
      <event start="T97-756" end="T30">Tudi to sem, o() </event>
      <event start="T30" end="T29">tudi o tem sem razmišljala, </event>
      <event start="T29" end="T102-146">tako da, v bistvu najbolj mi je pomagalo to, da ne preveč napakiram, </event>
      <event start="T102-146" end="T107-792">zaradi tega ker sem ful eem ... [glas] </event>
      <event start="T107-792" end="T31">eee ful velikokrat rada preveč napakiram, </event>
      <event start="T31" end="T112-98">sploh kar se tiče potovanj. </event>
      <event start="T112-98" end="T32">Eem in sem </event>
      <event start="T32" end="T121-011">namerno sem si naredila, eem katera oblačila oziroma katere cote bom imela gor. </event>
      <event start="T121-011" end="T123-911">Oziroma k() kaj bom nosila vsak dan gor. </event>
      <event start="T123-911" end="T34">In pol sem si pač tis() tiste cote not napakirala </event>
      <event start="T34" end="T132-941">in eee mi je to ful fajn ideja bila. </event>
      <event start="T139-613" end="T140-631">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T140-631" end="T144-457">In pol smo leteli prvo do Istanbula. </event>
