      <event start="T180-458" end="T47">Eee </event>
      <event start="T47" end="T48">ampak okej. </event>
      <event start="T48" end="T183-849">Sva j() na koncu sva jo izpeljala. </event>
      <event start="T186-051" end="T49">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T49" end="T186-936">Točno to. </event>
      <event start="T190-341" end="T51">Ja v bistvu, </event>
      <event start="T51" end="T192-222">pač. </event>
      <event start="T192-222" end="T52">[glas] F() [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T52" end="T195-991">ful je smešno, </event>
      <event start="T195-991" end="T199-360">zaradi tega ker fora je, da je pač na totem faksu, </event>
      <event start="T199-360" end="T53">eee </event>
      <event start="T53" end="T205-373">s katerim smo imeli pač toto nnn nnn I guess izmenjavo narejeno, </event>
      <event start="T205-373" end="T207-884">eem ji pač ... </event>
      <event start="T207-884" end="T212-818">[glas] Vsako leto dobijo določeno količino denarja. </event>
      <event start="T212-818" end="T54">In pol toti denar morajo nekod ponucati, </event>
      <event start="T54" end="T215-865">a ne. </event>
      <event start="T215-865" end="T221-042">In toti denar eee ga toto leto niso ponucali pač dosti hitro </event>
      <event start="T221-042" end="T55">in so mogli na hitrico nekako ponucati denar </event>
      <event start="T55" end="T56">in pol so bili tako: </event>
      <event start="T56" end="T225-441">"Okej, </event>
      <event start="T225-441" end="T231-092">gremo našim prijateljem iz Slovenije nekako posodit toti denar." </event>
      <event start="T231-092" end="T57">In so nam eem sofinancirali potovanje na Japonsko, </event>
      <event start="T57" end="T238-812">tako da nas je bilo pol osem izbranih. </event>
      <event start="T238-812" end="T241-52">In smo šli pol na Japonsko. [glas] </event>
      <event start="T247-043" end="T60">Eee ja ne, </event>
      <event start="T60" end="T61">eee </event>
      <event start="T61" end="T62">kriterij je bil to, da smo mogli napisati eno tako mini seminarsko o eem naravnih nesrečah, </event>
      <event start="T62" end="T258-66">in jaz sem itak da pisala o poplavah, ko so bile na Koroškem. </event>
      <event start="T258-66" end="T261-358">Eem. [zvok] </event>
      <event start="T261-358" end="T63">Eem ... in ... </event>
      <event start="T63" end="T64">pol so pa gledali še ocene. </event>
      <event start="T64" end="T65">Tako da ja, </event>
      <event start="T65" end="T268-962">tota ... </event>
      <event start="T268-962" end="T272-105">eee tota seminarska pa pol ocene. </event>
      <event start="T272-105" end="T278-744">[premor] [nerazumljivo] </event>
      <event start="T278-744" end="T280-88">Halo? [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T282-305" end="T282-746">Aja. [smeh] </event>
